&lt;h1 id=&#34;connection-to-real-learning&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#connection-to-real-learning&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Connection to Real Learning&lt;/h1&gt;
